         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 3rd May ¶  ¶ 1895 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you that Messrs Minchin and C. French Jr., ¶ Charles H. French. ¶  ¶ Herbarium Assistants in my Branch, who were employed for about ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.05.03</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Charles Topp</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">B95/3533, unit 830, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written by G. Luehmann and signed by M.</p>
               </note>Melbourne, 3rd May<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1895</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you that Messrs Minchin and C. French Jr.,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles H. French.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Herbarium Assistants in my Branch, who were employed for about three months in the Agricultural Department, returned to my Office this morning and resumed their former duties.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On 2 May 1895 the Secretary<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for Agriculture, David Martin, wrote to Topp: 'In compliance with your request of 1st inst I have instructed Mr French Jr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to report himself to the Government Botanist tomorrow, and Mr Minchin has also been instructed that, as the work for which he was obtained has been completed, he should report himself to the Govt Botanist'. Topp forwarded this letter to M 'for his information' on 6 May and M replied the same day: 'I am grateful to the Undersecretary for arranging the return of the two Herbarium Assistants, who — as reported already, reported themselves back on Friday-morning, the 3th [<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">sic</seg>]<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>inst, and resumed their work here'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Govt. Botanist.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Under Secretary</p>
         </div>
